{"title":"fix: correct vigil-app Deployment selector typo","body":"Root cause: Deployment selector in git manifest has typo 'vigil-app-typo' that doesn't match template labels 'vigil-app', causing immutable field conflict during Flux reconciliation.

Evidence: "Deployment/default/vigil-app dry-run failed (Invalid): Deployment.apps \"vigil-app\" is invalid: [spec.template.metadata.labels: Invalid value: {\"app\":\"vigil-app\"}: `selector` does not match template `labels`, spec.selector: Invalid value: {\"matchLabels\":{\"app\":\"vigil-app-typo\"}}: field is immutable]"

This fix corrects the selector matchLabels from 'vigil-app-typo' to 'vigil-app' to match the template labels, resolving the immutable field conflict."}
